&lt;li&gt;Be a mentor and provide hands-on coaching and professional development for Renewal Managers and CSMs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create processes, set best practices and build replicable patterns for go to markets initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help scale the Growth Customer Success segment through automations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
